### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json
@token = your-jwt-token-here

### Get All Movies
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies

### Get Movie by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/movie_1

### Search Movies by Title
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/search?query=dark

### Search Movies by Genre
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/search?genre=action

### Search Movies by Year
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/search?year=1994

### Search Movies with Multiple Filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/movies/search?genre=sci-fi&year=2010

### Add New Movie (requires authentication)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/movies
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Blade Runner 2049",
  "genre": ["sci-fi", "thriller", "drama"],
  "year": 2017,
  "description": "A young blade runner's discovery of a long-buried secret leads him to track down former blade runner Rick Deckard.",
  "director": "Denis Villeneuve",
  "actors": ["Ryan Gosling", "Harrison Ford", "Ana de Armas"],
  "rating": 8.0
}

